{"tid":47051,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺唔覺連登仔話舊高登仔唔肯接受新野好反感","createTime":"2016-12-20T05:41:16.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T08:05:13.000Z","uid":1858,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"70e106238633e6749510e5ab28e64efd732834a8","tid":47051,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:41:16.000Z","msg":"我本身對於lihkg呢個新壇係好開心同好認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但自從成班5p狗入左嚟之後就開始有d反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家個邀請碼系統拉曬d 5p，mk入黎（雖然我都係用邀請碼，但係我高登ac本身用isp註冊,同依家同名）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成班狗入曬嚟都算，新會員咪慢慢習慣呢到囉<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，點知個個帶曬d 5p文化入嚟，又吾又甘咁，比人屌都仲可以反駁番話新壇應該接受新事物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，同班大陸人黎香港周街坐周街柯屎再話我地唔接納佢地有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，最好笑係會有人認同佢地，幫佢地還擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，有人走去整新icon將腦魔emoji化，其實此舉已經剝削曬腦魔嘅精髓。近排又走多個肥婆icon出黎。平心而論，你地咁做嘅好意同心機我都明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但始終出到嚟嘅觀感都唔多討好。但呢個時候班又有班人走出黎話我地唔接受新野。如果我地係唔接受新野，咁苦笑icon點走出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時唔係話唔接受新野，但係高登固有文化就一定要保留。連高登文化都捍衛唔到仲點捍衛香港文化，抵抗蝗蟲入侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後，請你班新會員咪再話我地唔接受新野，你要記住依家係你地踩入黎我地地頭，唔通變相要我地就番你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b534b240bb2ef52847997ab383493f9c3bef7c1","tid":47051,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:43:39.000Z","msg":"苦笑icon原產地係高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d61a38baa561531be5520c07ad26234c157923f","tid":47051,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:44:15.000Z","msg":"#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"4dc188cf2fd5f71b55f5ef45141da6906900d4fa","tid":47051,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:44:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>苦笑icon原產地係高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我知，係你傑作丫麻"},{"pid":"fdac43a86372d9f2b9b0f80438ddecf486532ae8","tid":47051,"uid":1773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9045c7c6525dbbf9e655f8f165390654be298abb","tid":47051,"uid":49866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"